片公審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222172222573-1222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161222%2Fbkn-20161222172222573-1222_00822_001.html&d=m6%2BIrinw8%2B9tR7N%2FW6xkEGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=13215a71\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161222/bkn-20161222172222573-1222_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a0e4ba06d3dbf597219b3125134d7c611d121c","tid":50583,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"951193b341d87768819b38e84f5d73095bd190cd","tid":50583,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://ON9.CC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FON9.CC&d=m6%2BIrinw8%2B9tR7N%2FW6xkEGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=03b43d21\" target=\"_blank\">http://ON9.CC</a>真係ON9 點解飲益力多唔屌得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通細枝就唔算違例？洗唔洗話幾多毫升以上先檢控？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你知唔知條例點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家講緊飲益力多有冇違例 你走去講條例點黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得香港人奴性重<br />\n有例唔理合唔合理都要守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcbc140b0df8b0196b4742090b8c03a1e81895b","tid":50583,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:23:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>響隻手度！<br />\n<br />\n響個口度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><